constituent: banquet, relax, house, sun, day, tongue wagging, woman
heisigStory: To carry on from the last frame, we note the entire day of work that comes between a woman and her house in preparing for a dinner banquet, pictorially "interrupting" her relaxation.
koohiiStory1: The WOMAN spent all DAY preparing a banquet in the HOUSE.
koohiiStory2: Under the roof, all day long, the woman prepared for the banquet (this wording helps me remember the order of this kanji´s elements).
myStory: bữa tiệc. người phụ nữ ở nhà cả ngày vì bữa tiệc
